\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1\b\f0\fs24\lang9 Luna Game Toolkit\par
\b0\fs16 The easy, fast and fun 2D game development framework!\par
Allows you make games and other multimedia applications in Object Pascal.\par
\b\fs20 Overview\par
\b0\fs16 The Luna Game Toolkit\'99 (LGT) represents a premier independent toolkit tailored for the creation of 2D games utilizing Embarcadero Delphi\'ae, optimized for desktop PCs operating on Microsoft Windows\'ae and leveraging OpenGL\'ae for enhanced hardware-accelerated rendering.\par
Crafted for robust performance and user-friendly operation, LGT is versatile enough to facilitate the development of a wide array of 2D gaming genres and graphical simulations. It offers a straightforward and intuitive API, enabling rapid and efficient project development. The toolkit encompasses comprehensive support for textures, audio sampling, music streaming, video playback, and the capability to load resources seamlessly from compressed and encrypted archives, among other features. With LGT, the experience of game development is streamlined, swift, and enjoyable.\par
